observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:

Require the Municipal Accountant to ensure that all disbursements are accompanied by proper documentation;

And the Municipal Treasurer to require from the suppliers/contractors Sales Invoices or Official Receipts for any goods delivered and services rendered in accordance with the mandates of Presidential Decree (PD) No. 1445, BIR Revenue Regulation No. 18-2012, and COA Circular No. 2004-006; 

Also, strengthen internal controls to enhance transparency and accountability, thus mitigate the risk of financial irregularities and uphold the Municipality's integrity in its financial operations. Additionally, require the Municipal Treasurer to secure the Official Receipts/Sales Invoices and submit the same to the Municipal Accountant for the latter to immediately provide to the Audit Team to avoid audit suspension.

